<p>Every Airbnb host receives negative reviews eventually. What matters is <strong>how you respond</strong>.</p>
<p>At iHousing, we've maintained 4.8+ average ratings across 100+ properties by mastering professional review management.</p>
<p>This guide shows you our proven strategies for handling negative feedback and protecting your hosting reputation.</p>
<hr class="my-8">
<h2>The Impact of Reviews: By The Numbers</h2>
<h3>Why Review Management Matters</h3>
<table>
  <thead>
